---
title: Shrimp Taco Lettuce Wraps with Smoky Chipotle Beans, Charred Fajita Veggies, and Garlic-Lime Crema
description: Tender Boston lettuce makes for the perfect low-carb vehicle for tacos. A touch of chipotle powder adds a distinct smokiness to the equation. If heat isn’t your thing, a cool garlic-lime crema and creamy avocado are there to cool things off .
